Client|RiseClient|IntentClient|ThunderHack|Wurst|BleachHack|Baritone|Kami|Exhibition|PrestigeClient|DoomsdayClient|Asteria|ArgonClient|XenonClient|GypsyClient|VirginClient|CatleanClient|Hellion|Krypton|devkrypton|skidkrypton|TokenLogger|TokenGrabber|SessionStealer|DiscordToken|Webhook|RemoteAccess|ReverseShell|Backdoor|KeyLogger|C2Server|dqrkis|dqris|dqrkisxyz|dqrisxyz|5138134200|orgchainlibs|imgui|imguibinding|imguigl3|imguiglfw|jnativehook|JNativeHook|GlobalScreen|NativeKeyListener"

                        $hasAdvancedDecodeContext = $hasDecoderShape -and $hasCheatContext
                    }

